Date: Fri, 29 Feb 2008 00:44:00 +0000
From: David Howells <>
Subject: [PATCH 05/37] Security: Change current->fs[ug]id to current_fs[ug]id() [ver #34]
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
X-Mailing-List: linux-kernel@vger.kernel.org
X-Lkml-Link: https://lkml.org/lkml/2008/2/28/481

Change current->fs[ug]id to current_fs[ug]id() so that fsgid and fsuid can be
separated from the task_struct.
Signed-off-by: David Howells <dhowells@redhat.com>
Reviewed-by: James Morris <jmorris@namei.org>
---
